Step 2:-

Create a Measure to Check Moving Average is Correct or NOT.

MovingAvgCheck =
VAR Period = 
    CALCULATETABLE(
        SUMMARIZE('Calendar', 'Calendar'[Month], 'Calendar'[MIndex], 'Calendar'[Year]),
        DATESINPERIOD('Calendar'[Date], MAX('Calendar'[Date]), -3, MONTH)
    )

RETURN

CONCATENATEX(
    Months,
    FORMAT([Total Sales], "0.0"), 
    ","
) & " / " & COUNTROWS(Period)

